Source: netbiff
Section: mail
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Jeff King <peff@acm.org>

Package: netbiff
Architecture: any
Recommends: netbiff-backend
Description: Mail notification utility
 Netbiff is an enhanced version of the traditional biff, featuring
 multiple connections, user-defined biff/reset actions, and backend
 support for many mail clients.
 .
 This package contains no files. You will need to select a netbiff client
 and appropriate backend(s).

Package: netbiff-backend
Architecture: any
Recommends: netbiff
Description: Mail notification utility backend
 Netbiff is an enhanced version of the traditional biff, featuring
 multiple connections, user-defined biff/reset actions, and backend
 support for many mail clients.
 .
 This package contains no files. You will need to select a netbiff client
 and appropriate backend(s).

Package: netbiff-client-text
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: netbiff-backend
Provides: netbiff
Conflicts: netbiff-client-gtk
Replaces: netbiff-client-gtk
Description: Text-based mail notification utility
 Netbiff is an enhanced version of the traditional biff, featuring
 multiple connections, user-defined biff/reset actions, and backend
 support for many mail clients.
 .
 This package contains the text-based netbiff client.

