Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: netbiff-backend
Provides: netbiff
Conflicts: netbiff-client-text
Replaces: netbiff-client-text
Description: GTK-based mail notification utility
 Netbiff is an enhanced version of the traditional biff, featuring
 multiple connections, user-defined biff/reset actions, and backend
 support for many mail clients.
 .
 This package contains the GTK-based netbiff client.

Package: netbiff-backend-imap
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: netbiff
Provides: netbiff-backend
Description: IMAP backend for netbiff
 Netbiff is an enhanced version of the traditional biff, featuring
 multiple connections, user-defined biff/reset actions, and backend
 support for many mail clients.
 .
 This backend supports connection to IMAP servers for the retrieval
 of mail information.

Package: netbiff-backend-file
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: netbiff
Provides: netbiff-backend
Description: Filesystem backend for netbiff
 Netbiff is an enhanced version of the traditional biff, featuring
 multiple connections, user-defined biff/reset actions, and backend
 support for many mail clients.
 .
 This backend supports the examination of data through file system
 attributes to determine updates.

